#: ../../source/vuln/cmdinjection.rst:2
msgid "命令注入"
msgstr "Command Injection"

#: ../../source/vuln/cmdinjection.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/vuln/cmdinjection.rst:6
msgid "命令注入通常因为指Web应用在服务器上拼接系统命令而造成的漏洞。"
msgstr ""
"Command injection usually refers to vulnerabilities caused when a web "
"application concatenates system commands on the server."

#: ../../source/vuln/cmdinjection.rst:8
msgid "该类漏洞通常出现在调用外部程序完成一些功能的情景下。比如一些Web管理界面的配置主机名/IP/掩码/网关、查看系统信息以及关闭重启等功能，或者一些站点提供如ping、nslookup、提供发送邮件、转换图片等功能都可能出现该类漏洞。"
msgstr ""
"This type of vulnerability often appears when external programs are called "
"to implement functionality. Examples include web management interfaces for "
"configuring hostnames, IP addresses, masks, and gateways, viewing system "
"information, shutting down or restarting systems, and sites that provide "
"ping, nslookup, mail sending, image conversion, and similar features."

